   <h1>The Troll&#39;s Bane Chronicle</h1>

   <h2>The third year of the new era: June</h2>

<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 1st Agons gift shop opens again.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 2nd Kincent Nolatri and Pronom Palmsugar organise the festival "Days of Duel", a fighting contest. The winner is Trice.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 2nd a feast for Tanora is proposed because of the drought. But it doesn't take place.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 2nd Brendan Mason discovers ancient scrolls in the library, which tell that ogres hoard every food in their caves during the drought. A hint on the disappeared animals. Search expeditions for the cave are started.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 3rd Leinad talks about a Necromancer, who summoned Undeath in front of his eyes. It is supposed to be Darlok..</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 4th a hoard of ogres  attacks Troll's Bane and the town wall stands her first acid test. Hagen von Rabenfeld and Dhalsim distinguish themselves at the defence. It is assumed that there is more behind this attack. One day later ogres attack again.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 5th the wedding of Andriel and Dhalsim was held.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 6th King Tialdin appoints the dwarf Josef as Inquisitor.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 6th the Clan of the Axe joins the Lyrenzia Foundation as ninth guild.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 9th the lack of water in the rivers, caused by the drought, makes itself felt.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 9th Kincent Nolatri claims to have been bitten by a vampire. As turned out, this was only invented to attract attention.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 10th Grant Herion starts a search operation for the secret ogre cave.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 11th the town as attacked again by some ogres, who apparently were on the search for food.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 12th Leinad calls  up to a expedition, that has made the cartography of the isle to its business.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 13th Lyria Argante announce her engagement to Ultoris. </p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 14th Elvin calls up to hoard goods and food, because everything indicates a drought of long duration..</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 14th Nerevar Schattenaxt puts a bounty on "werewolves". As turned out, the affected ones, Arvon and Sunny Holz, had only eaten rotten mushrooms.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 15th the ogre cave is finally found and the imprisoned animals are freed after long time. An imprisoned hobbit, Necrophobius Funguis, and an ogre woman in search for her king are said to be involved into this  affair.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 16th Demli Dongan is accused of stealing a great amount of potions from the king of Silverbrand, Tialdin. </p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 16th the priestess Elaralith is accused by several people of stealing.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 18th Belegi Zahar is appointed into the Council of Wise of the Clan of the Axe.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 19th a mysterious rumour writer turns up, who blames Aragon ben Galwan of having an affair with Lyria Argante. </p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 22nd Josefine returns to Troll's Bane after a long journey.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 23rd Sunny Holz leaves the isle by boat. Some unknown persons make fun of him with anonymous notes at the board.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 24th the annulment of Ultoris' engagement with Lyria Argante is announced.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 25th a unknown person with the pseudonym "Jello Biafra" questions Tialdin's reign and calls him a shepherd. According to rumors the unknown person is the dwarf Ingrain.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 26th L&uacute;thien Falassion puts up a message, because she searches for a woman called Malinne..</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 27th Hagen von Rabenfeld warns the town of the dangerous thief Ferdinand Kohlberg, who holds up citizens at work and robs them.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 28th it is rumoured that Tialdin secretly bills and coos with the human lady Tifareth.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 29th Obolon searches for the best carpenter of Illarion..</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 29th Xaveria finds a mysterious book about a necromancer called Verashnia.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 30th Tenchi Mahou searches for a teacher of magic. Morgaine le Fay accepts the offer.</p>
<p>In the year three of the new era on June, the 30th Malinne leaves the isle by boat. According to own statements she never will return.</p>

